sidered when methotrexate is used with other potentially hepatotoxic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/141/', '', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, More', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Simeprevir, Amprenavir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, Etravirine, Dolutegravir, Cobicistat, More', 1767369485);
