tion with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/200/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Simeprevir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, More', 'Paritaprevir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Oseltamivir, Brincidofovir, Elbasvir, Voxilaprevir, Pibrentasvir, Rimantadine, Telbivudine, Efavirenz, More', 1767369485);
